The paper deals with a cross-modal matching problem between text and images, specifically for person search. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) domains. The paper also involves attention mechanisms and pose information, which are common topics in information retrieval (cs.IR), multimedia (cs.MM), and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
